<article id="post-65135" class="post-65135 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-sophoslabs-uncut category-threat-research tag-coronavirus tag-covid-19 tag-malware tag-patch-tuesday tag-phishing tag-ransomware tag-scams tag-spam region-en-us">

		<div class="md:mt-16 container mt-8">
