<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>These and additional IOCs will be added to our <a href="https://github.com/sophoslabs/covid-iocs">GitHub repository</a>.</p>
<p>And it was inevitable that someone would eventually create a ransomware and <a href="https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/new-coronavirus-ransomware-acts-as-cover-for-kpot-infostealer/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">call it Coronavirus</a>.</p>
<p><a href="https://news.sophos.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/corona-ransom-1.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-65301 size-large" src="https://news.sophos.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/corona-ransom-1.png?w=640" alt="" width="640" height="265" srcset="https://news.sophos.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/corona-ransom-1.png 715w, https://news.sophos.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/corona-ransom-1.png?resize=300,124 300w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></a></p>
